13
00:01:26,752 --> 00:01:37,024
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

14
00:01:37,024 --> 00:01:41,216
=Love on the Turquoise Land=

15
00:01:41,216 --> 00:01:44,000
(This story is a work of fiction)

16
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:47,056
=Episode 6=

17
00:01:57,258 --> 00:02:00,336
(Toxic and Hazardous)

18
00:03:45,642 --> 00:03:48,802
Mad Blade sits in the central tent.

19
00:03:50,003 --> 00:03:53,122
Once entering the Twilight Chasm,

20
00:03:53,962 --> 00:03:58,362
fiends hunt human monsters.

21
00:04:00,763 --> 00:04:05,923
Blades and hounds
walk the Turquoise Land,

22
00:04:07,242 --> 00:04:12,682
and Ghost Whip cracks his glowing whip.

23
00:04:17,322 --> 00:04:19,083
Are you a South Mountain Hunter?

24
00:04:21,442 --> 00:04:22,603
Just wait.

25
00:04:23,442 --> 00:04:25,122
When Mad Blade arrives,

26
00:04:25,762 --> 00:04:27,603
your membranes will be split open,

27
00:04:28,483 --> 00:04:30,283
your rotten guts

28
00:04:31,163 --> 00:04:35,163
spilled to the sun.

29
00:04:35,523 --> 00:04:36,362
Listen to me.

30
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,483
I'm not an Earth Fiend.

31
00:04:37,483 --> 00:04:38,523
I'm here to help you.

32
00:04:38,723 --> 00:04:42,643
Seven hounds, two whips, and one blade.

33
00:04:43,762 --> 00:04:47,083
The Golden Gate
is fortified beyond defeat.

34
00:04:48,043 --> 00:04:50,643
Blades, hounds, and whips unite.

35
00:04:50,643 --> 00:04:55,643
None of you invaders will return alive.

36
00:04:58,723 --> 00:04:59,483
Have some water.

37
00:04:59,483 --> 00:05:00,843
Take your time. Speak slowly.

38
00:05:12,843 --> 00:05:17,802
A patrol checks
the Golden Gate every fourth year.

39
00:05:18,762 --> 00:05:24,002
No more wrongful deaths in Nanba.

40
00:05:56,643 --> 00:05:57,923
In this greenhouse of ours,

41
00:05:59,002 --> 00:06:01,122
the catalytic spray
activates periodically.

42
00:06:01,442 --> 00:06:04,723
It significantly improves
medicinal herb grafting success.

43
00:06:05,122 --> 00:06:07,283
But it's extremely harmful to humans.

44
00:06:07,843 --> 00:06:09,322
Hence the alarm system.

45
00:06:09,643 --> 00:06:10,283
See?

46
00:06:11,122 --> 00:06:12,682
The spraying will start any minute.

47
00:06:13,643 --> 00:06:15,362
You need to figure out quickly

48
00:06:15,362 --> 00:06:16,603
how to explain this to me.

49
00:06:23,923 --> 00:06:25,802
Am I the General Manager
of Roadsound Group?

50
00:06:26,202 --> 00:06:27,043
Yes.

51
00:06:28,403 --> 00:06:30,723
Then why do I always
feel like an outsider?

52
00:06:32,283 --> 00:06:34,163
I know less
about core operations and personnel

53
00:06:34,163 --> 00:06:35,483
than you do.

54
00:06:36,643 --> 00:06:37,523
I get it now.

55
00:06:38,643 --> 00:06:39,643
So,

56
00:06:39,643 --> 00:06:41,963
you're conducting field research?

57
00:06:42,362 --> 00:06:42,923
Right?

58
00:06:56,483 --> 00:06:57,643
You're hiding things from me.

59
00:06:58,442 --> 00:07:01,403
Since I first met Ms. Lin as a kid,

60
00:07:01,442 --> 00:07:02,843
she hasn't aged a single day.

61
00:07:03,603 --> 00:07:04,242
Xiong,

62
00:07:04,403 --> 00:07:06,322
you've fought hard for the group

63
00:07:06,723 --> 00:07:08,682
and taken serious injuries
multiple times, right?

64
00:07:09,002 --> 00:07:10,403
But after resting for a few days,

65
00:07:10,523 --> 00:07:11,523
you recover completely.

66
00:07:11,523 --> 00:07:12,603
Do you think I buy that?

67
00:07:13,603 --> 00:07:15,083
I don't care what you're developing

68
00:07:15,603 --> 00:07:17,322
or if it's supposedly to protect me.

69
00:07:17,322 --> 00:07:18,562
But I'm not a child anymore.

70
00:07:18,562 --> 00:07:19,723
Nor am I a fool!

71
00:07:19,802 --> 00:07:21,603
I'm part of this family too!

72
00:07:29,762 --> 00:07:31,202
I won't be a mascot anymore,

73
00:07:31,723 --> 00:07:34,002
playing cards with this CEO

74
00:07:34,322 --> 00:07:35,762
or fishing with that president.

75
00:07:49,043 --> 00:07:50,083
To reach this day,

76
00:07:57,163 --> 00:08:00,122
to become my true self,

77
00:08:00,562 --> 00:08:02,122
I've exhausted myself.

78
00:08:06,562 --> 00:08:07,322
If...

79
00:08:07,643 --> 00:08:09,242
If I can't...

80
00:08:10,442 --> 00:08:13,562
If I can't become one of you,

81
00:08:18,442 --> 00:08:19,083
then today...

82
00:08:19,802 --> 00:08:20,923
let's end this all.

83
00:08:23,643 --> 00:08:24,283
Let me...

84
00:08:27,002 --> 00:08:27,802
finally...

85
00:08:28,682 --> 00:08:29,442
be free.

86
00:09:09,763 --> 00:09:11,442
Ms. Lin, you understand Yan Tuo best.

87
00:09:12,202 --> 00:09:14,763
The "invite-the-enemy-into-jar" trick
worked perfectly.

88
00:09:16,482 --> 00:09:17,562
He went to the farm?

89
00:09:19,363 --> 00:09:21,763
His reaction suggests no suspicion.

90
00:09:22,442 --> 00:09:24,643
Just curiosity and wanting to belong.

91
00:09:25,403 --> 00:09:27,842
But if we keep lying,

92
00:09:28,923 --> 00:09:30,202
and he discovers something

93
00:09:30,202 --> 00:09:31,842
and then confronts you about it,

94
00:09:32,883 --> 00:09:33,602
that'll be worse.

95
00:09:34,283 --> 00:09:35,763
Speak your mind directly.

96
00:09:37,363 --> 00:09:38,883
Once he truly understands

97
00:09:38,883 --> 00:09:41,482
he's not like us,

98
00:09:42,283 --> 00:09:43,602
he'll have two choices.

99
00:09:44,562 --> 00:09:45,722
Either assimilate

100
00:09:46,043 --> 00:09:47,082
or leave.

101
00:09:48,802 --> 00:09:52,243
Assimilation requires
full disclosure from you.

102
00:09:52,243 --> 00:09:53,403
No reservations.

103
00:09:54,643 --> 00:09:56,123
If he chooses to leave,

104
00:09:57,562 --> 00:09:59,163
we have to eliminate him.

105
00:09:59,602 --> 00:10:01,243
He's not a blood bag after all.

106
00:10:02,802 --> 00:10:03,523
Ms. Lin,

107
00:10:04,962 --> 00:10:06,602
it's time to decide.

108
00:10:09,403 --> 00:10:13,923
Whether we let the fox
in the henhouse remains uncertain,

109
00:10:15,202 --> 00:10:19,962
but it's time to lure the enemy out.

110
00:10:30,058 --> 00:10:32,656
(Nanshan Rescue Team,
Xicang City, Yanguan Province)

111
00:10:38,682 --> 00:10:39,442
You see,

112
00:10:39,763 --> 00:10:41,043
this is where we treat injuries

113
00:10:41,043 --> 00:10:42,202
at the base.

114
00:10:42,283 --> 00:10:43,682
Conditions aren't hospital-grade.

115
00:10:44,243 --> 00:10:45,682
And this is the best equipment

116
00:10:45,682 --> 00:10:47,082
we can get.

117
00:10:49,523 --> 00:10:51,802
Mrs. Hua is in a stable condition now.

118
00:10:52,283 --> 00:10:54,923
Let's arrange shifts then.

119
00:10:55,082 --> 00:10:55,962
Keep a close eye.

120
00:10:56,962 --> 00:10:59,123
All right. I'll take
the first shift tonight.

121
00:10:59,523 --> 00:11:02,003
Ma Hanzi and I are usually
at the base most of the time.

122
00:11:02,523 --> 00:11:03,842
He's familiar with this place.

123
00:11:04,283 --> 00:11:05,283
He can take more shifts.

124
00:11:06,283 --> 00:11:07,802
Our top priority right now is

125
00:11:07,962 --> 00:11:09,602
to find out any news about Mr. Crip.

126
00:11:13,202 --> 00:11:14,243
What's up, Jiang?

127
00:11:15,602 --> 00:11:16,523
It's from the hospital.

128
00:11:17,482 --> 00:11:18,802
They said they received

129
00:11:19,482 --> 00:11:20,842
a letter addressed to Mrs. Hua.

130
00:11:21,562 --> 00:11:22,523
The head nurse mentioned

131
00:11:23,602 --> 00:11:25,082
the envelope reads,

132
00:11:25,923 --> 00:11:27,482
"To the South Mountain Hunters,

133
00:11:28,523 --> 00:11:30,082
from an old friend at the Golden Gate."

134
00:11:43,883 --> 00:11:45,243
Since you like cats so much,

135
00:11:45,602 --> 00:11:48,643
why not properly adopt a pretty one?

136
00:11:48,923 --> 00:11:50,482
This scruffy calico cat

137
00:11:50,802 --> 00:11:51,842
eats and runs.

138
00:11:52,043 --> 00:11:53,363
It won't even let us pet it once.

139
00:11:55,003 --> 00:11:56,442
In the feline world,

140
00:11:56,722 --> 00:11:58,322
calicos are seen as the most beautiful.

141
00:11:58,682 --> 00:11:59,602
Don't you think it is

142
00:11:59,602 --> 00:12:01,043
independent and full of character?

143
00:12:01,842 --> 00:12:03,003
Free-spirited

144
00:12:03,043 --> 00:12:04,363
and reliant on no one.

145
00:12:04,482 --> 00:12:06,562
Then it shouldn't come here
for free meals.

146
00:12:06,602 --> 00:12:07,763
Let it catch mice itself.

147
00:12:09,202 --> 00:12:11,043
That's exactly what makes it remarkable.

148
00:12:11,962 --> 00:12:13,283
No begging or groveling,

149
00:12:13,842 --> 00:12:15,363
yet it makes people care about it

150
00:12:15,363 --> 00:12:16,523
and want to pamper it.

151
00:12:16,763 --> 00:12:17,883
By your logic,

152
00:12:17,962 --> 00:12:19,523
when young people date,

153
00:12:19,962 --> 00:12:22,202
they should learn from stray cats?

154
00:12:23,403 --> 00:12:24,322
Not exactly.

155
00:12:25,163 --> 00:12:26,403
If humans acted like that,

156
00:12:26,403 --> 00:12:27,802
they'd become rather annoying.

157
00:12:33,842 --> 00:12:35,482
(Nobody)
(New updates. Same spot tonight?)

158
00:12:41,582 --> 00:12:42,082
Thank you.

159
00:12:42,082 --> 00:12:42,722
Enjoy your meal.

160
00:12:43,082 --> 00:12:43,763
You came.

161
00:12:54,163 --> 00:12:55,842
How did you know my favorite dishes?

162
00:12:56,442 --> 00:12:57,442
You're a regular here.

163
00:12:58,163 --> 00:12:59,123
The owner knows.

164
00:13:02,763 --> 00:13:04,883
How did she know who you meant?

165
00:13:06,243 --> 00:13:07,123
I asked her,

166
00:13:07,682 --> 00:13:09,283
"The exceptionally beautiful lady

167
00:13:09,283 --> 00:13:10,523
with sharp-tongued remarks

168
00:13:10,883 --> 00:13:12,523
and an artistic appearance,

169
00:13:13,043 --> 00:13:15,722
but hiding countless secrets.

170
00:13:15,842 --> 00:13:16,962
What did she usually order?"

171
00:13:18,082 --> 00:13:19,322
She recognized you instantly.

172
00:13:20,763 --> 00:13:22,163
So that was a compliment?

173
00:13:23,602 --> 00:13:25,082
What does Mad Blade mean?

174
00:13:26,802 --> 00:13:27,523
Mad Blade.

175
00:13:33,202 --> 00:13:36,523
A performing troupe
calls their year-end finale

176
00:13:36,562 --> 00:13:37,523
Closing the Chest.

177
00:13:38,003 --> 00:13:39,602
A footballer's farewell match

178
00:13:39,602 --> 00:13:40,722
is Hanging Up the Boots.

179
00:13:41,163 --> 00:13:41,842
So, I think

180
00:13:42,163 --> 00:13:43,883
it means retirement from the world

181
00:13:43,883 --> 00:13:44,763
of combat.

182
00:13:47,722 --> 00:13:48,403
Fine.

183
00:13:49,243 --> 00:13:50,923
Keep your secrets if you must.

184
00:13:51,763 --> 00:13:52,883
I just want you to know

185
00:13:52,883 --> 00:13:54,682
they're deeply concerned
about Mad Blade.

186
00:13:56,722 --> 00:13:58,202
This intel's on the house.

187
00:13:58,202 --> 00:13:59,442
Not included in the tally.

188
00:14:07,482 --> 00:14:08,163
Thanks.

189
00:14:08,923 --> 00:14:10,043
Shall we cut to the chase?

190
00:14:14,403 --> 00:14:15,283
I located the man.

191
00:14:16,482 --> 00:14:17,082
Where?

192
00:14:20,562 --> 00:14:21,523
Heavily guarded.

193
00:14:21,923 --> 00:14:24,163
Probably tortured too.

194
00:14:24,403 --> 00:14:25,523
His mind's gone foggy.

195
00:14:26,003 --> 00:14:27,363
But he's tight-lipped.

196
00:14:27,682 --> 00:14:28,523
He disclosed nothing.

197
00:14:31,923 --> 00:14:32,962
How can you be sure

198
00:14:33,482 --> 00:14:34,363
that the one you found

199
00:14:34,363 --> 00:14:35,682
is the one I mentioned?

200
00:14:40,043 --> 00:14:42,523
Disabled left calf, correct?

201
00:14:51,202 --> 00:14:54,003
Mad Blade... It's a person, isn't it?

202
00:14:55,802 --> 00:14:57,003
What's your real angle here?

203
00:14:57,322 --> 00:14:58,003
He said

204
00:14:58,883 --> 00:15:01,482
Mad Blade could pierce
the Earth Fiends' membranes,

205
00:15:02,202 --> 00:15:04,202
exposing their guts to daylight.

206
00:15:06,043 --> 00:15:06,842
Therefore, Mad Blade

207
00:15:06,842 --> 00:15:09,082
must be your trump card
against the Earth Fiends.

208
00:15:11,763 --> 00:15:13,363
Not discussing this today.

209
00:15:14,763 --> 00:15:16,643
Only matters I care about.

210
00:15:17,123 --> 00:15:18,123
The man I want to save.

211
00:15:20,482 --> 00:15:21,003
Understood.

212
00:15:23,643 --> 00:15:25,082
He's still valuable to Lin Xirou.

213
00:15:25,322 --> 00:15:26,763
No immediate danger.

214
00:15:28,442 --> 00:15:29,283
But Xiong Hei

215
00:15:29,283 --> 00:15:31,243
threatens how long that'll hold.

216
00:15:31,523 --> 00:15:33,043
If you want to save him, act fast.

217
00:15:34,202 --> 00:15:36,043
Also, I need to make this clear upfront.

218
00:15:36,283 --> 00:15:37,802
In fact, I want to help you.

219
00:15:38,003 --> 00:15:39,003
But this matter

220
00:15:39,163 --> 00:15:40,722
has made Xiong Hei suspect me.

221
00:15:41,403 --> 00:15:42,403
At this point,

222
00:15:42,403 --> 00:15:44,363
I consider the mission accomplished.

223
00:15:44,883 --> 00:15:46,682
Now, it's your turn to pay
per our agreement.

224
00:15:48,363 --> 00:15:49,322
No need to remind me.

225
00:15:53,802 --> 00:15:54,482
Say it.

226
00:15:58,962 --> 00:15:59,722
Next time,

227
00:16:00,602 --> 00:16:02,883
whenever and for whatever reason,

228
00:16:03,003 --> 00:16:04,003
if I ask to meet you,

229
00:16:04,202 --> 00:16:05,243
you can't refuse.

230
00:16:17,722 --> 00:16:19,722
All of you are indispensable.

231
00:16:20,082 --> 00:16:22,322
They're trying
to wipe us all out at once.

232
00:16:24,082 --> 00:16:25,682
Inviting all of us

233
00:16:25,682 --> 00:16:27,123
shows they've got a solid plan.

234
00:16:28,482 --> 00:16:29,923
No dirty tricks, a straight fight.

235
00:16:30,283 --> 00:16:31,123
We fear nobody.

236
00:16:31,643 --> 00:16:32,722
At the ice factory,

237
00:16:33,082 --> 00:16:34,482
we were ambushed,

238
00:16:34,883 --> 00:16:36,202
which led to Mrs. Hua's injury.

239
00:16:36,802 --> 00:16:37,682
Underhanded tactics

240
00:16:37,962 --> 00:16:38,962
are their specialty.

241
00:16:40,562 --> 00:16:41,363
Then what do we do?

242
00:16:41,722 --> 00:16:42,802
Mrs. Hua's unconscious,

243
00:16:43,043 --> 00:16:43,842
and Mr. Crip...

244
00:16:49,283 --> 00:16:50,403
Show of hands.

245
00:16:51,163 --> 00:16:51,842
Go or not?

246
00:16:54,562 --> 00:16:55,523
I absolutely must go.

247
00:16:57,082 --> 00:16:58,482
I missed out last time,

248
00:16:59,202 --> 00:17:00,682
so I'm definitely going this time.

249
00:17:02,043 --> 00:17:03,322
Would anyone actually skip this?

250
00:17:43,843 --> 00:17:44,923
Mr. Crip has been captured.

251
00:17:46,323 --> 00:17:48,163
If you still won't take action,

252
00:17:49,762 --> 00:17:51,083
consider this visit nonexistent.

253
00:17:56,563 --> 00:17:57,242
Time?

254
00:17:58,083 --> 00:17:58,722
Location?

255
00:17:59,762 --> 00:18:01,643
You should join our operation.

256
00:18:02,442 --> 00:18:02,962
That way...

257
00:18:02,962 --> 00:18:04,163
I told Jiang.

258
00:18:05,202 --> 00:18:06,603
After this mission ends,

259
00:18:06,603 --> 00:18:07,682
I'll quit completely.

260
00:18:08,163 --> 00:18:09,123
When peace returns,

261
00:18:10,603 --> 00:18:12,002
you can make new plans.

262
00:18:12,722 --> 00:18:14,202
But now that enemies have emerged,

263
00:18:14,603 --> 00:18:16,403
how could we not have the Mad Blade?

264
00:18:20,123 --> 00:18:21,682
We both have our own duties

265
00:18:21,682 --> 00:18:22,843
and desires.

266
00:18:24,002 --> 00:18:25,442
I won't interfere with your choices,

267
00:18:26,202 --> 00:18:27,722
and I hope you'll respect mine.

268
00:18:28,923 --> 00:18:30,323
Send me the time and place.

269
00:18:31,282 --> 00:18:32,202
I'll be there on time.

270
00:18:39,482 --> 00:18:40,403
Tomorrow's a day off.

271
00:18:40,563 --> 00:18:42,123
I'll go to an art exhibition downtown.

272
00:18:42,323 --> 00:18:43,202
What about you?

273
00:18:48,363 --> 00:18:49,563
Not in good form today.

274
00:18:50,123 --> 00:18:51,403
Wrapped in a hide,

275
00:18:51,403 --> 00:18:52,643
the fiend bone is scentless.

276
00:18:55,323 --> 00:18:56,682
I'll try it alone tomorrow.

277
00:18:56,682 --> 00:18:57,962
Tomorrow's a day off.

278
00:18:58,323 --> 00:18:59,722
There's an art exhibition downtown.

279
00:18:59,722 --> 00:19:00,242
I want to go.

280
00:19:00,682 --> 00:19:01,682
What's your plan?

281
00:19:06,083 --> 00:19:07,002
I heard.

282
00:19:07,962 --> 00:19:08,962
Go by yourself then.

283
00:19:10,923 --> 00:19:11,883
