285
00:19:16,962 --> 00:19:17,643
Luo.

286
00:19:20,482 --> 00:19:21,682
You know about Huoquan Pills?

287
00:19:24,923 --> 00:19:25,563
Yes.

288
00:19:26,123 --> 00:19:27,762
