297
00:19:58,123 --> 00:19:59,242
Huoquan Pills,

298
00:19:59,682 --> 00:20:01,042
the hunters' ancient formula,

299
00:20:02,002 --> 00:20:03,282
clear nasal passages,

300
00:20:04,002 --> 00:20:05,202
remove congestion

301
00:20:05,883 --> 00:20:07,643
and help one detect fiends miles away.

302
00:20:11,482 --> 00:20:14,242
But effects and toxicity coexist.

303
00:20:16,163 --> 00:20:18,442
A clear nose brings blindness.

304
00:20:19,403 --> 00:20:20,403
Inferior medicine.

305
00:20:23,603 --> 00:20:24,563
Best left unconsumed.

306
00:20:27,042 --> 00:20:28,123
May not be fully blind.

307
00:20:28,482 --> 00:20:29,403
I've researched.

308
00:20:30,002 --> 00:20:32,522
Huoquan Pills only
dilate pupils in daylight,

309
00:20:32,762 --> 00:20:33,843
blinding glare vision.

310
00:20:34,282 --> 00:20:36,083
Night vision remains.

311
00:20:36,522 --> 00:20:38,323
All Mad Dog candidates

312
00:20:38,682 --> 00:20:41,843
can choose to take the pills or not,

313
00:20:43,002 --> 00:20:46,002
but consumption
doesn't guarantee selection.

314
00:20:47,242 --> 00:20:50,323
Consequences are your own.

315
00:20:55,323 --> 00:20:56,123
Jiang,

316
00:20:58,123 --> 00:20:59,123
I've made up my mind.

317
00:21:00,962 --> 00:21:01,803
Don't you want

318
00:21:03,242 --> 00:21:04,442
to talk to Luo first

319
00:21:05,323 --> 00:21:06,522
and hear what she thinks?

320
00:21:09,123 --> 00:21:10,242
Becoming a Mad Dog

321
00:21:11,123 --> 00:21:13,202
is about becoming
a stronger South Mountain hunter

322
00:21:14,722 --> 00:21:16,202
to protect everyone better.

323
00:21:26,123 --> 00:21:28,042
