328
00:22:02,163 --> 00:22:03,442
someone other than me?

329
00:22:05,242 --> 00:22:06,083
Or rather

330
00:22:08,363 --> 00:22:09,923
before you came here,

331
00:22:12,482 --> 00:22:13,762
among your own kind,

332
00:22:15,843 --> 00:22:16,883
was there anyone

333
00:22:19,123 --> 00:22:20,603
